    "description": "Three.. Two.. One.. Get Ready.. Go! Step inside the arena and have a blast! Match up with other players and make friends, use your arms to move about, and engage in immensely fun mini-games in the most explosive VR party game - Blast Circus!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/fb71f9a94066f218d9994824e1bff414.poster.avif?t=1733872716\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/fb71f9a94066f218d9994824e1bff414.webm?t=1733872716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/fb71f9a94066f218d9994824e1bff414.mp4?t=1733872716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Step inside the arena, a beautifully made venue that offers the most explosively fun mini-games in VR gaming!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/8c580b3cd33af65a94c602450a1ef7d9.poster.avif?t=1733872716\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/8c580b3cd33af65a94c602450a1ef7d9.webm?t=1733872716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/8c580b3cd33af65a94c602450a1ef7d9.mp4?t=1733872716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Oh, you don’t have legs! Make the best of your space, move your arms, and flail about to move around! Start in the Obstacle Course to practice your kinetics!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/bec363f76bc9c99fcb7f6e5189364c3f.poster.avif?t=1733872716\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/bec363f76bc9c99fcb7f6e5189364c3f.webm?t=1733872716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/bec363f76bc9c99fcb7f6e5189364c3f.mp4?t=1733872716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The party won’t start with just you! Matchmake with other players, interact and talk via voice chat, team up, and make friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/2df9bec84520b14375eb98f893222013.poster.avif?t=1733872716\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/2df9bec84520b14375eb98f893222013.webm?t=1733872716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341520/extras/2df9bec84520b14375eb98f893222013.mp4?t=1733872716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Juggle bombs, dodge cannon fire, deflect fireballs, and more! Tons of mini-games such as Spin the Cannon, Fireball Hockey, Floor is Lava, Grapple Mania and many others will ensure endless fun VR parties in Blast Circus!",
